description:
* Parent issue: https://gitlab.com/groups/gitlab-org/-/epics/3766
* ~frontend counterpart: https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/issues/271226

## Summary

This is to add support for Authentication, Request headers and excluded urls fields to the query component.

## Designs

* Figma file: https://www.figma.com/file/7CaJqOTOpPEOzkYkoU5bs5/DAST-Ondemand-Profile

## Implementation plan

* [x] Update `DastSiteProfiles`
  * [x] add support for request headers and excluded urls
  * [x] add support for authentication details
* [x] Update specs

```diff
--- proposal_iteration1.graphl
+++ proposal_iteration2.graphl
@@ -2,12 +2,26 @@ query DastSiteProfiles($fullPath: ID!, $after: String, $before: String, $first: Int, $last: Int) {
  project(fullPath: $fullPath) {
    siteProfiles: dastSiteProfiles(after: $after, before: $before, first: $first, last: $last) {
      pageInfo {
        ...PageInfo
      }
      edges {
        cursor
        node {
          id
          profileName
          targetUrl
          editPath
          validationStatus
+         auth {
+           enabled
+           url
+           usernameField
+           passwordField
+           username
+         }
+         excludedUrls
+         requestHeaders
+       }
      }
    }
  }
}
```
